('Meenakshi Amman Temple', 'Tamil Nadu', 'A historic Hindu temple in Madurai, dedicated to Goddess Meenakshi. A masterpiece of Dravidian architecture.', 'Low', 'High', 'High', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/Meenakshi_Amman_Temple_Entrance_Sculpture.JPG', 'Pilgrimage'),
