('Tirupati Balaji Temple', 'Andhra Pradesh', 'A famous Hindu temple dedicated to Lord Venkateswara, the most visited place of worship in the world.', 'Low', 'High', 'High', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/ff/Tirumala_Venkateswara_Temple.jpg', 'Pilgrimage'),
('Kashi Vishwanath Temple', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'One of the most famous Hindu temples dedicated to Lord Shiva, located on the western bank of the Ganges.', 'Low', 'High', 'High', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a3/Kashi_Vishwanath_Temple_Varanasi.jpg', 'Pilgrimage'),
