('Jaisalmer Fort', 'Rajasthan', 'One of the largest fully preserved fortified cities in the world, a "living fort" with shops, hotels, and houses inside.', 'Medium', 'High', 'Medium', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/05/Jaisalmer_Fort_sunset_view.jpg', 'Historical'),
